1. *Zla* stvar je što ne znamo kako da rešimo ovaj problem. (The bad thing is that we don't know how to solve this problem.)
2. Ona je postupala *zlo* prema njemu. (She acted badly towards him.)
3. Ona je potpuno *zla*. (She is completely evil.)
4. Ona se *zlo* ponašala. (She behaved badly.)
5. *Zla* sreća je nekada bila deo života. (Bad luck used to be part of life.)
6. Mi smo imali *zlu* vest. (We had bad news.)